{"tid":1438353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對付福健幫策略","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:26:44.000Z","uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3f530fd739cf4b3fb6958e4b4eb23e1960a782","tid":1438353,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"其實俾晒啲資料啲狗先，當然一定要有證據證明你俾過啲資料佢哋，如果到時有一大班可疑人士出入北角，而啲狗又唔做嘢，咁咪又俾人嘈多鑊。如果的狗拉人，就由得佢哋互相死過。一舉兩得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有英皇道395號果楝嘢，要用多部航拍機晨早mon到夜晚，睇下有冇人由果度攞棍攞刀出黎。果日再搵啲晌附近酒店做既手兄報料，睇下幾時有大批客走出嚟。再用航拍機影低佢哋行蹤。之後俾啲狗拉人。"},{"pid":"c97fd89f0de239fcf076cfb570493bfa20776836","tid":1438353,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efdf0aba2895c6d01939446c016b5f6bed56bef","tid":1438353,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"【811港島東大遊行】 10號下晝4點半將進行上訴聆訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438318/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【811港島東大遊行】當日維園會照有集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438329/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrmcoLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrmcoLA.jpg&h=b4db3112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港島東集會<br />\n日期：2019年8月11日(星期日)<br />\n時間：下午1時正<br />\n地點：維多利亞公園4至6號足球場<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情有待通知<br />\n<br />\n集會以和平理性方式進行，要求政府正面回應五大訴求，唯警方選擇以種種理由拒絕遊行申請，無疑令人有感政府嘗試打壓市民的遊行權利和自由，因此我們呼籲市民更加要站出來，繼續遍地開花，堅守五大訴求。"},{"pid":"b35de68fa7f4f110d2f8e8e6aceddaa51c6e9f60","tid":1438353,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5530ce17da5496ed9e56eda6d187507ad774dc35","tid":1438353,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1eef6f64122d635bef5cc7a4a9ef9f121bea5ae9","tid":1438353,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:49:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n香港人重點日程：<br />\n8月9-11日：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)<br />\n8月10日：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n8月10日：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n8月10日：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）<br />\n8月11日：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n8月11日：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFF4YRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFF4YRE.jpg&h=539785ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Lc7Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Lc7Li.jpg&h=8d1626e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFLHLw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFLHLw8.jpg&h=d8fae00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaMsLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaMsLz.jpg&h=b4f4136d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1PqYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1PqYA.jpg&h=5a975883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEdSDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEdSDA.jpg&h=da0e19d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/276scxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F276scxO.jpg&h=78ce765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af95J0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf95J0h.jpg&h=5304a0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2270b719622c3fe078bb050ab3a3854789516045","tid":1438353,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"push"}]}